item.title: Follow along at Airconf 2014
item.description: Airconf 2014 I will be presenting at 10:00 AM EST on August 14, 2014 by Google Hangout. The repository for the presentation is github.com/brianmhunt/Airconf-2014-Knockout. You can follow the presentation and review snippets used at brianmhunt.github.io/airconf-2014.
